---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout metadata={{ title: 'About' }}>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-12 prose">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <p>
      Hi, I’m [Student Name], a photographer based in [Location]. I enjoy capturing moments, exploring new places, and
      experimenting with light and color.
    </p>

    <p>
      This portfolio highlights a selection of my recent work across portraits, landscapes, and creative projects. I’m
      always learning, always exploring, and always looking for the next story to tell through my lens.
    </p>

    <img src="/images/about/me.jpg" alt="Kate Ferriter" class="rounded-xl shadow-md mt-8" />

    <p>
      When I’m not behind the camera, I’m usually editing photos, studying new techniques, or finding inspiration in
      everyday life. Or just hanging with my friends.
    </p>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
